description:
Add to turnkey's flake.nix:

  flake.lib = {
    defaultTellerLib = inputs.teller.lib;
    defaultTellerRegistry = system:
      (import inputs.nixpkgs {
        inherit system;
        overlays = [ inputs.teller.overlays.default inputs.toolbox.overlays.default ];
      }).turnkeyRegistry;
  };

Additive change — no consumer or module behavior changes yet. After this, 'nix eval .#lib' surfaces both outputs and they're reachable as inputs.turnkey.lib.defaultTellerLib / inputs.turnkey.lib.defaultTellerRegistry from any downstream flake.

Spot-check: nix eval .#lib --apply 'lib: lib.defaultTellerLib != null' should return true.
